  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>You can enjoy a large buffet breakfast with plenty of choice including hot options like eggs and bacon. Evening meals are a choice of four courses including a salad buffet.</p>
<p>The hotel’s restaurant serves up local dishes using fresh produce sourced in the South Tyrol region. These are complimented by a choice of international and Italian wines from the hotel’s cellar. After dinner, the bar offers a social and comfortable place to relax with a drink.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
