  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Val Gardena Active Programme partner accommodation</strong></p>
<p>Hotel Somont is an affiliate of the <a rel="noopener" href="https://www.valgardena-active.com/en/summer" target="_blank">Val Gardena Active</a> programme so you can join free or discounted activities every day of the week (activities are bookable and payable locally).</p>
<p><strong>Hotel facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Indoor pool with whirlpool</li>
<li>Spa with steam bath, sauna and relaxation area (open 3pm to 7pm) </li>
<li>Free spa towels</li>
<li>Free Wi-Fi </li>
<li>Parking garage (payable locally)</li>
</ul>]]></facilityDescription>
