  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>CIR Rooms</strong> are about 23m² and sleep two people. They're finished in an alpine style and have plenty of space. They have a shower. </p>
<p><strong>Sasslong Rooms</strong> are about 26m² and sleep up to three people (extra bed is a single or sofa bed). They have a shower.</p>
<p><strong>Dolomiti Rooms</strong> are about 28m² and sleep up to four people (extra bed is a sofa bed or single beds). They have plenty of space and a bath or shower. These rooms are available on request, please call to book.</p>
<p><strong>CIR Double Rooms for sole use</strong> are available on request, please call to book. </p>
<p>Please specify twin or double beds at the time of booking</p>
<p><strong>All rooms have:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Balcony</li>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>Bathrobes and slippers</li>
<li>Safe</li>
</ul>
<p>Cots are available for approx. €30 a day (bookable and payable locally) </p>
<p><strong>Local fees and taxes</strong></p>
<p>A resort tax of approx. €3.40 per person per night is payable locally.</p>
<p><strong>Accessibility</strong></p>]]></roomsDescription>
